text:
Dost,

Tere saath jo last discussion hua tha IITK mein Hall-5 Phatta ground me woh mera memoir hai(especially woh baat ki hum humesha ek dusre ke liye ready rahenge help krne ke liye whatever the situation we would be in). And saari baate tere saath aisi hi thi. We didn't spend that much time together par jo bhi hue woh humesha best the. We always pulled each others leg on a topic jo kisi ka tha hi nahi (tera tha waise xD) . üòûüòè

Tu bahut mast hain bhai, dil se humesha aisa hi rehna. Ek baat bolunga tu life mein bahut bakchodiya machaega bas tu apne comfort zone se thoda bahar aa kyoki tu bahut jyada acha achieve kr sakta hain.
Thanks for welcoming me to your room anytime. Tere room me bulla kaatne me maza toh bahut aata hai yaadein hain waha meri "ex" ki  :P
Tere saath GOA pending hain! Jald hi milte hain aur kahi chalte hain!!
author: Yadu  Sharma

text:
Ankur mere dost,
"Abe kal exam hai kya??" Yeh expression ka answer tere pass hi hota tha mere.
Baaki eco ke syllabus and exam se ek din pehle ki planning ki kaise answer ka jugaad krna hai. Wing ki bakchodiyan, and woh party toh zindagi mein humesha yaad rahegi, bahut hi mast maula hai tu bhai, and HUMESHA aisa hi rahiyo, kabhi kabhi ekdum se short packets mein teri energy nikalti rehti hai. 
Baaki I will always remember this quote by you, "A day may come when the courage of men fails, when we forsake our friends and break all bonds of fellowship, but it is not this day. This day we fight!!....."
Milte rahenge aage bhi bhai, harr saal ek baar minimum milne ka wada kiya hai WING A5 ne pura toh hoga hi woh!
Love you brother ‚ù§Ô∏è
author: Yadu  Sharma

text:
Dost,
Thanks for the wonderful memory jo Antaragni 3rd year mein banayi hain!! NATIONALS VS HOSPI ke sessions woh toh bahut hi epic the, humesha yaad aaenge who sessions [BTW Hospi >>>>> Nationals :)]
Milte hai jaldi!!
author: Yadu  Sharma

text:
Tere kuch followers bol rahe the mere subscribers kamm hai!

Jab tu khaega, MAZA aaega, phir tu bhaiya hi bhiaya gayega!!
author: Yadu  Sharma

text:
Man, you are one of the most humble person, I have met in IITK. I know ki tu life mein bahut bakchodiyan karega! Bas dhuaon mein yaad rakhna bhai :) 
Cheers to this journey. Thanks man for being the part.
author: Yadu  Sharma

text:
Sharmiji,
Bahut late mulakat hui aapse par kaafi bakchod hui. Last 2 months toh yaad rahenge jab sharmaji Nihal ke room aka "Hall-12 ka Mandir" mein aakr chup chaap meditation krte the. 
And thanks for coping up with me during those such high intensity trips :)
Btw Congrats bhai for IIMA(Chaapu toh tu hai hi!!). Stay connected bro! üçª
author: Yadu  Sharma

text:
Gowti,
Suna toh bahut tha tere baare mein, tere art ke baare mein. We met very late on our campus journey, par koi BT nahi. Gowti humesha hi yaad rahega tu, last 2 months and your way of explaining things(bahut hi interesting hain).
I will always remember that look that you had on your face(Pabhu Deva vibe) on 2nd April in Hall-5 phatta ground. I will never forget that day, and what we all experienced. Thanks gowti, jaldi milte hain, let's drop!!
author: Yadu  Sharma

text:
Jatin mere bhai,
First year me agar tum nahi hote toh hum dost kaise hote. ECONS trip kya jazab plan kari thi tune bhai. Manali mein raat ko peg maarkr mall road pr nikalna yeh ehaas dila diya tha ki yeh launde hain toh bahut mast and yaari atrangi toh hogi hi. Tabse toh kitne hi kisse banne hain A6 terrace par, chandra ke ghar, and aakri 2 month campus mein <3 (Jaipur ke liye sorry bro. Meri taraf se ek TRIP pending hain JAIPUR ki!! Is bvaar last time baar jaisi BT nahi xD)

Lucknow to campus tak journey uss UP roadways bus ki toh kaise hi bhulunga, pata hi nahi chala tha us din ki kab campus pahuch gaye. Milte rahenge bhai aage bhi and woh eco wali party aage bhi hoti rahegi! 
Tere saath random trip pr chalna hai and for sure. Near future mein chal rahe hain apan. Veere love you!
author: Yadu  Sharma

text:
Barwal,
Campus ke pehle dost, mujhe exactly yaad hain tu Hall-12 mess mein mila tha pehli baar aur tab apna Jaipur se belong krne wala discussion hua. Tabse toh kya hi bakchodi kari hain bhai. Saath me exam time padhne se teri aayashiyaan. Tere saath journey humesha yaad rahegi chahe who HEC tenure ki ho yaa saath me drams ki yaa endless bulla session yaa  teri mausi ki. Mausi ke liye toh ek ticket black me bechi thi(xD). Tune bhai itne efforts maare hain mere liye. Thanks bhai :)
HEC mein Galaxy me bahut ladai hui and planning bhi, bahut hi memorable the woh experiences.  Aur just Galaxy ke baad UPSC ki preparation, I always respect you for that decision. Terese jyada dedicated banda meine nahi dekha hain apne campus life mein. Tune bahut baar padhai ke liye bulla sessions and apne faltu dicussion ignore kare hain, mujhe bhi bahut baar room se nikala hain. Par uske baad I always knew ki hum ache dost hain. 
Trust me tu jaldi IAS officer banne wala hain. Bhul mat jaana bhai. Aata hu COVID ke baad ghar pr tabtak prep krle exam ki.
Time bahut kamm tha likhne mein isliye pura likh nahi paaya bhai, bahut hain tere baare mein likhne ko, pr you were always my friend. Milte hain!!
author: Yadu  Sharma
